steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitdash004" and Comment "Testing"
When I navigate to menu "Dashboard app" without submenu
Then I should see Dashboard screen display
Then I should see table Name "jitdash004" displayed in dashboard list
When I select table Name "jitdash004" in dashboard table list
When I toggle on switcher of item "Create of" with table Name "jitdash004"
Then I should see option value "jitdash004s.updated_at,jitdash004s.created_at" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Params to request" index "1" of item "Create of" with table Name "jitdash004"
When I select multi dropdown label "Params to request" index "1" of item "Create of" with table Name "jitdash004" by value "jitdash004s.created_at"
Then I should see option value "jitdash004s.updated_at" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Params to request" index "1" of item "Create of" with table Name "jitdash004"
Then I should NOT see option value "jitdash004s.created_at" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Params to request" index "1" of item "Create of" with table Name "jitdash004"
